      "span_text": "Surface potential arises from the total dipole moment of a monolayer system from three components; the dipole moment at the hydrophobic region (lipid tail), the polar region of the lipid molecules (head), and the aqueous subphase adjacent to the lipid molecules [CITATION_1] ."
